Info.Title: John Doe: Vigilante
Info.Writer: Stephen M. Coates (screenplay), Stephen M. Coates (story), Kelly Dolen (story)
Info.Actors: Jamie Bamber, Lachy Hulme, Gary Abrahams, Sam Parsonson
Info.Plot: An ordinary man fights violence the only way he knows how - by killing one criminal at a time. Hero or villain? Justice or vengeance? You decide.
